                  "text": "Accept"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "declined",
                  "text": "Decline"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendAcceptDecline",
              "text": "It's up to you to head over to Victoria Island, but a Knight-in-Training that can't take care of one's self in battles is likely to cause harm to the Empress's impeccable reputation. As the Head Tactician of this island, I can't let that happen, period. I want you to keep training until the right time comes."
            },
            "id": "askAccept",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
